snippet.title: THE DARK DWELLERS - RELEASE TRAILER
snippet.description:
AVAILABLE NOW ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1771620/The_Dark_Dwellers/

In this dank pit of rot and undeath, take control of The Mortali, the newest member of ragtag-group THE DARK DWELLERS. Fight and crawl your way through this subterranean land, collect unique weapons, learn devastating Blood Magic spells and attempt to end The Maddening Curse.
